videos.headline: Neal sheds tackle for early Syracuse TD
videos.description: Moe Neal breaks a tackle and punches it in for a 23-yard Syracuse touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Neal sheds tackle for early Syracuse TD) 2019/09/21

videos.headline: Syracuse fakes the pitch, scores on quick shovel pass
videos.description: Syracuse QB Tommy DeVito fools the defense and shovels the ball to Aaron Hackett for a 10-yard score.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Syracuse fakes the pitch, scores on quick shovel pass) 2019/09/21

videos.headline: DeVito goes untouched for 36-yard TD
videos.description: Syracuse QB Tommy DeVito finds a hole and sprints 36 yards for the touchdown.

videos.headline: Bellamy's 47-yard TD gets Western Michigan on the board
videos.description: LeVante Bellamy takes the handoff and explodes through the hole to get Western Michigan on the board.

videos.headline: Jackson sheds tacklers with vicious stiff arm for Cuse TD
videos.description: Trishton Jackson catches the quick pass, then breaks several tackles en route to a 46-yard Syracuse touchdown.
